OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776179469
OL,3,CTwo teenagers dead after crash on M1
OL,5,FTwo teenagers have died following a
OL,6,Fcrash on the M1 southbound shortly
OL,7,Fbefore junction 20 in Leicestershire.
OL,9,FPolice were called at 1.33pm on Friday
OL,10,F10 April following a report that a
OL,11,Fblue car, travelling along Gilmorton
OL,12,FLane towards Lutterworth, had left the
OL,13,Froad bridge above the carriageway and
OL,14,Fcollided with a minibus travelling
OL,15,Fsouthbound on the M1.
OL,17,FLeicestershire Fire and Rescue Service
OL,18,Fand East Midlands Ambulance Service
OL,19,Falso attended the scene.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
