OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776179469
OL,3,CTwo teenagers dead after crash on M1
OL,5,FFour people in the minibus ` a white
OL,6,FFiat Ducato ` were taken to hospital
OL,7,Fwith non-life-threatening injuries.
OL,8,FThe driver, a man, has been discharged
OL,9,Fand three women remain in hospital.
OL,11,FThe two people in the blue car, both
OL,12,Fteenagers, were declared dead at the
OL,13,Fscene.
OL,15,FThe road is likely to remain closed
OL,16,Ffor a number of hours yet while
OL,17,Fforensic work continues to be carried
OL,18,Fout.
